    <h1>Dr. Mix – Concrete Mix Design</h1>
    <p><strong>Professional concrete mix design application up to 60 MPa.</strong></p>

    <h2>App Description</h2>
    <p>
      Dr. Mix is a professional concrete mix design tool developed for civil engineers,
      QC engineers, batching plant operators, and precast factories.
      The app performs accurate concrete mix calculations using engineering standards
      and built-in data.
    </p>

    <h2>Key Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Concrete mix design up to 60 MPa</li>
      <li>Supports slump and flowable concrete</li>
      <li>Automatic calculation of cement, water, admixtures, Fly Ash, Microsilica, and GGBS</li>
      <li>Automatic water–cement ratio calculation</li>
      <li>Printable and shareable PDF reports</li>
      <li>Works fully offline</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>
      Dr. Mix does not collect, store, or share any personal data.
      All calculations are performed locally on the user’s device.
      No internet connection is required.
    </p>

